{"priority": "major", "kind": "bug", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}ts=1694483"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "gazebo", "full_name": "osrf/gazebo", "uuid": "{51a0cd5d-8697-4eb1-8b08-e919ee881e1c}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/286/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/286.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/286/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/286/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/286/allow-sdf-conversion-across-different"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/gazebo/issues/286/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "John Hsu", "uuid": "{0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec/5445ce6e-6273-47f0-84eb-621c86ca11cb/128"}}, "nickname": "hsu", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec"}, "title": "Allow SDF Conversion across different elements", "component": null, "votes": 0, "watches": 2, "content": {"raw": "For example, [sdf conversion from sdf 1.0 to sdf 1.2](#!/osrf/gazebo/src/c8974309a98df2fe9bb6c7cdb9f5c74866caf535/gazebo/sdf/1.2/1_0.convert?at=default) allows remap within an element.  To expand conversion to inter-element nodes, e.g.\r\n~~~\r\n<world>\r\n  <physics>\r\n    <update_rate>1</update_rate>\r\n  </physics>\r\n</world>\r\n~~~\r\nto\r\n~~~\r\n<world>\r\n  <real_time_update_rate>1</real_time_update_rate>\r\n  <physics>\r\n  </physics>\r\n</world>\r\n~~~\r\n\r\nmight require something like below:\r\n~~~\r\n  <convert name=\"world\">\r\n    <move>\r\n      <from>\r\n        <convert name=\"physics\">\r\n          <src element=\"update_rate\"/>\r\n        </convert>\r\n      </from>\r\n      <to>\r\n        <dst element=\"real_time_update_rate\"/>\r\n      </to>\r\n    </move>\r\n  </convert>\r\n~~~\r\nMore examples in [physics_sdf_refactor branch](#!/osrf/gazebo/src/ed00985423b86f4838ae31841a1dcba96c56332c/gazebo/sdf/1.4/1_3.convert?at=physics_sdf_refactor).", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>For example, <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/src/c8974309a98df2fe9bb6c7cdb9f5c74866caf535/gazebo/sdf/1.2/1_0.convert?at=default\" rel=\"nofollow\">sdf conversion from sdf 1.0 to sdf 1.2</a> allows remap within an element.  To expand conversion to inter-element nodes, e.g.</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">&lt;world&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;physics&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;update_rate&gt;</span>1<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/update_rate&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/physics&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/world&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>to</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><span class=\"nt\">&lt;world&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;real_time_update_rate&gt;</span>1<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/real_time_update_rate&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;physics&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/physics&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"nt\">&lt;/world&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>might require something like below:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span>  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;convert</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;world&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;move&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;from&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"nt\">&lt;convert</span> <span class=\"na\">name=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;physics&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">&gt;</span>\n          <span class=\"nt\">&lt;src</span> <span class=\"na\">element=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;update_rate&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/convert&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/from&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;to&gt;</span>\n        <span class=\"nt\">&lt;dst</span> <span class=\"na\">element=</span><span class=\"s\">&quot;real_time_update_rate&quot;</span><span class=\"nt\">/&gt;</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/to&gt;</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/move&gt;</span>\n  <span class=\"nt\">&lt;/convert&gt;</span>\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>More examples in <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/src/ed00985423b86f4838ae31841a1dcba96c56332c/gazebo/sdf/1.4/1_3.convert?at=physics_sdf_refactor\" rel=\"nofollow\">physics_sdf_refactor branch</a>.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Ian Chen", "uuid": "{eaa6fca5-6deb-43f6-907f-971c144735dd}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7Beaa6fca5-6deb-43f6-907f-971c144735dd%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7Beaa6fca5-6deb-43f6-907f-971c144735dd%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:10b01d41-a2e9-4a41-a907-e6e2f03b6cd5/1e4adcdf-1946-4280-9aea-eb5f15a7f912/128"}}, "nickname": "Ian Chen", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:10b01d41-a2e9-4a41-a907-e6e2f03b6cd5"}, "state": "closed", "version": {"name": "all", "links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/gazebo/versions/225575.json"}}}, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2012-12-06T23:05:57.388185+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2016-09-14T19:43:55.414467+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 286}